data.description: Beautiful newly re-modeled home situated in a convenient location, this home offers ease of access to amenities, schools, and major transportation routes. As you step inside, you will be greeted by a spacious living area, providing ample room for relaxation and entertainment, natural light fills the interior, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere and with central air conditioning, you'll stay comfortable year-round. Lower electricity costs thanks to the addition of solar panels. Enjoy the luxury of new flooring throughout the entire home, giving it a fresh and modern feel with soft close cabinets and drawers all through out. Outside the fenced backyard offers both privacy and convenience. The garage offers a large space with a tall ceiling that includes shelfs, extra wide and with tall ceiling for plenty of storage.
